    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been absolute gold to me. It's in really solid shape\u2014runs super smooth and has plenty of life left for your next big adventure! I've taken great care of it, and it's just looking for a new home and someone new to hit the road with. It\u2019s a reliable, comfy drive that won't let you down. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
